Package: psHarmonize
Title: Creates harmonized dataset based on set of instructions
Version: 0.2.8
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Stephen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "John.Stephen@northwestern.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7309-9193"))
Description: Creates harmonized dataset from multiple different datasets. Uses a harmonization sheet as a set of coding instructions. Package allows for long and/or wide dataset as output. Package also creates error log.
